on}}]]\n{{French presidential election, 2017}}\n\n=== First round ===\n==== By department ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable collapsible collapsed\" style=\"text-align:right; font-size:95%; line-height:20px;\"\n! width=\"200\" rowspan=\"3\"| [[Departments of France|Department]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Emmanuel Macron|Emmanuel<br/>Macron]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Marine Le Pen|Marine<br/>Le Pen]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Fran\u00e7ois Fillon|Fran\u00e7ois<br/>Fillon]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Jean-Luc M\u00e9lenchon|Jean-Luc<br/>M\u00e9lenchon]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Beno\u00eet Hamon|Beno\u00eet<br/>Hamon]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Nicolas Dupont-Aignan|Nicolas<br/>Dupont-Aignan]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Jean Lassalle|Jean<br/>Lassalle]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Philippe Poutou|Philippe<br/>Poutou]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Fran\u00e7ois Asselineau|Fran\u00e7ois<br/>Asselineau]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Nathalie Arthaud|Nathalie<br/>Arthaud]]\n! width=\"110\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Jacques Cheminade|Jacques<br/>Cheminade]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{En Marche!/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{National Front (France)/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{The Republicans (France)/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{La France Insoumise/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{Socialist Party (France)/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{Debout la France/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{Miscellaneous right/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{New Anticapitalist Party/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{Popular Republican Union/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{Workers' Struggle/meta/color}};\"|\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{Solidarity and Progress/meta/color}};\"|\n|-\n! Votes\n! %\n! Votes\